               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <title>Psalter (151 Psalms of David, fol. 1r-148v; 15 biblical canticles, fol. 149r-164v; Song of Songs, fol. 165r-173v; Praises of Mary, fol. 174r-187v; Gate of Light, fol. 187v-193r; Hymn to Mary, Angels are praising Mary. fol. 193r-194r)</title>
                     <note>Spiritual meanings for the Hebrew letters in Psalm 118, fol. 119v-128v; Columetric rubrication in Psalm 148, fol. 147r, Psalm 150, fol. 148r, and the tenth biblical canticle, fol. 159v-160v
                        
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <title>Image of Mary, fol. 196r-203r; Image of Jesus, fol. 203r-209v; Image of George, fol. 210r-215v; Image of Takla Hāymānot, fol. 216r-222v; Image of Gabra Manfas Qeddus, fol. 222v-224v; Image of Michael, fol. 225r-230v; Image of Gabriel, fol. 230v-233v; Image of Raguel, fol. 234r-239r; Greeting to the Icon of Mary, O tenderhearted, fol. 239v-241r
                        
                     </title>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <title>Miracles of Mary</title>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <title>Miracles</title>
                     <note>1 miracle of George, fol. 244r-245r; 1 miracle of Takla Hāymānot, fol. 245v-247r; 1 miracle of Gabra Manfas Qeddus, fol. 247r-248v; 1 miracle of Michael, fol. 248v-249r; 1 miracle of Gabriel, fol. 249v-250v; 1 miracle of Raguel, fol. 250v-252v
                        
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <title>Prayer to the Trinity for Emperor Menelik II
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ተማኅፀንኩ፡ ብክሙ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ በከመ፡ አተውክሙ፡ ቤተ፡ አብርሃም፡ ተዘከሩኒ፡ ለገብርክሙ፡ ምኒልክ፡ ከማሁ፡ አዕትውኒ፡ ውስተ፡ መንበርክሙ፡
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                     <title>Prayer to Jesus Christ, O Jesus Christ whose name is sweet
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ኦእግዚእየ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ጥዑመ፡ ስም፡ ወሕይወተ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዓለም፡ ይትከዓው፡ በላዕሌየ፡ ሞገደ፡ ምሕረትከ፡ ከመ፡ ይደምስስ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ዕዳየ።
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                     <title>Asmat prayers
                     </title>
                     
                  </msItem>   
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i8">
                     <title>Anaphora of Mary by Cyriacus of Behnesa
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">አኰቴተ፡ ቁርባን፡ ዘእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ድንግል፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ። ዘደረሰ፡ አባ፡ ህርያቆስ፡ ዘሀገረ፡ ብህንሳ
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem>               
               </msContents>
